  "text": "In addition to physiological processes, MMPs effects are also observed in a number of pathological processes such as arthritis, Alzheimer's disease, atherosclerosis, vascular disease, gastritis ulcer disease, central nervous system disease, liver cirrhosis, tumours and their metastasis (Fig. 2) . MMPs can be studied from different perspectives as markers of some cancer, neurodegenerative, immune and cardiovascular diseases [CITATION_1] .",
